Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世界是怎么了？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What is the world coming to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fuck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这么开始的:\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And that was how it started:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:29.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们五个因为捏造的罪名\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Five of us brought in on a trumped-up charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…被这些弱智关了进来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...to be leaned on by half-wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿我真不能多说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I really can't talk about it much here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:41.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察们永远也想不到，而我现在知道的是…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What the cops never figured out,and what I know now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:44.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…这些人永远不会被打垮，永不会被打倒\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...was that these men would never break,never lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不会屈服于任何人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Never bend over for anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都不行\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:03.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加州  圣佩德罗(当日)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是谁？  - 杰克・贝尔探员，FBI\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Who are you? - Agent Jack Baer, FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 死了多少人？ - 到现在发现15个\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- How many dead? - 15 so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:13.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还在继续打捞水下的尸体\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're still pulling bodies out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有生还者吗？  - 两个\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Any survivors? - Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个被送进了州立医院， 但他正在昏迷\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One guy's in County hospital,but he's in a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地方检察官带走了第二个家伙， 纽约来的跛子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The DA has a second guy,a cripple from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局长要封锁这地方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The chief wants this place sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么问题， 就给他打电话吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you have any questions, give him a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是戴夫・奎恩，我在洛杉矶， 星期二才回来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is Dave Kujan.I'll be in Los Angeles until Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:09.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若有急事，可联系圣佩德罗警署的杰夫・拉宾…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you need to reach me, contact Jeff Rabin of the San Pedro Police Department...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…拨内线112，祝你愉快\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...at extension 112. Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（圣佩德罗警局）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我为什么不能见他？  - 我说了…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Why can't I see him? - I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…地方检察官昨晚来这里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...the DA came down here last night ready to arraign...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…准备在移交州局前就提审他。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...even before they moved him to County.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:26.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟后，肯特的律师露面了…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kint's lawyer shows up five minutes later...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:29.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…地方检察官出来时像是被妖怪扇晕了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...the DA comes out looking like\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}the bogeyman smacked him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:32.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们接受了他的供述，与他达成协议\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They take his statement,and they cut him a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:36.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们控他什么罪名没？  - 非法持械，二级轻罪\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Did they charge him with anything? - Weapons, misdemeanor 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:42.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地方检察官能做到这样我给他点赞了，你懂吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I give the DA credit for getting that much,you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让一下，长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:49.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整桩事情开始有政治色彩 市长昨晚来过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This whole thing has turned political.The mayor was here last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:53.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有局长。今天早上州长也打了电话，知道吧？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The chief. This morning,the governor called, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:57.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你，这家伙受到高层黑暗势力的保护，\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm telling you, this guy is protected from up on high by the Prince of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 记住我说的话吧   - 他什么时候可保释外出？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Take my word for it. - When does he post bail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可能顶多再过两小时   - 我想要见见他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Maybe two hours, tops. - I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不行   - 我一定得见他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- No. - I gotta see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不，我做不到--   - 你必须得帮我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- No. I can't-- - You gotta do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:09.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大老远来就是为了这事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I came a long way for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴夫，拜托\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dave, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我让你见他， 他也不会跟你说的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Even if I let you talk to him,he won't talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:21.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会怀疑被录音的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's paranoid about being recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他知道审讯室里有线路   - 我戒了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- He knows the rooms are wired. - I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是审讯他，只不过是友好谈话罢了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This won't be an interrogation,just a friendly chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:30.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他不会进审讯室的  - 那就找别的地方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- He won't go into the interrogation room. - Then someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不行\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:38.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若这是毒品交易，那毒品呢？ 如果是袭击，那又是谁指使的？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If this was a dope deal, where's the dope?If it was a hit, who called it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:42.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这些问题在你心里已经有了一大堆疯狂的理论来回答\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm sure you have a host of wild theories to answer all these questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:45.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你很清楚我的想法   - 真是疯了，而且也没什么意义\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You know what I think. - That's crazy, and it doesn't even matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:48.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙已经得到完全豁免 他的背景也已经查出来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The guy's got total immunity.His story checks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:52.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他不知道你想知道的东西   - 我没认为他知道，并不完全知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- He doesn't know what you want to know. - I don't think he does, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他的事情远没有那么简单，相信我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But there's a lot more to his story,believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:59.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道为什么有27个人死在那个码头\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I wanna know why 27 men died on that pier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来与价值九千一百万的毒品有关 但毒品却不在那儿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...for what looks to be $91 million worth of dope that wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:07.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而最重要的是，我要确认迪恩・基顿的死讯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And above all,I want to be sure Dean Keaton's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他确实死了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了。就两小时。到他被保释就结束\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come on. Two hours.Just till he makes bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都死了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不在乎你说的这个基顿有多厉害…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't care how tough you say Keaton was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…那条船上没人能生还\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...nobody on that boat could've come out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:26.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他能说话吗？  - 他一小时前醒来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Is he talking? - He regained consciousness an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了些话，不是英语 然后就停下了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He spoke, not English, then he lapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是匈牙利话吗？  - 我不知道，也许是吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Hungarian? - That might have been it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们大部分是匈牙利人  - 你得把这穿上\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Most of them were Hungarians. - You gotta put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧伤病人很容易感染\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Burn victims are very susceptible to infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有，那儿是禁烟的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And, of course, there's no smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请戴上口罩，还有别去碰他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keep your mask up.Please don't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会死吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Is he gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他全身有六成被烧伤 肋骨断裂--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's burned 60 percent of his body,broken ribs--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫医院保安来.叫个人守在门口\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Call security. Put a man on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他会有危险？  - 对\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Is he dangerous? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:02.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约尔吗？我是贝尔 从洛杉矶给你打来的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Joel? Baer. Down at LA County.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:14.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在码头找到的那人 叫阿科西・卡瓦什\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look, the guy they pulled out of the harbor is Arkosh Kovash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我明白\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yes, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，他受了重伤\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, he's all fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听不清\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭会儿嘴好吗？我在打电话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Will you shut up? I'm on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:29.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，直至我派人来看着他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, not till I put a man on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派个会说匈牙利语的人来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Send me someone who can speak Hungarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他醒着 他说话就像泰国妓女\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's awake.He's talking like a Thai hooker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:36.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯撒・苏斯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keyser Soze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:39.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？  - 凯撒・苏斯！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What?- Keyser Soze!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:45.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到法院去找丹・曼厮固\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Call Dan Metzheiser over at Justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…还有海关的戴夫・奎恩\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and find Dave Kujan from Customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:30.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话痨，这是海关的奎恩探员\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Verbal, this is Agent Kujan from Customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:32.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:34.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想在你离开前问几个问题\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He wants to ask you a few questions before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么问题？  - 大部分是关于迪恩・基顿的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What about? - About a Dean Keaton, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:42.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想先由在纽约的指认谈起\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'd like to start at the lineup back in New York.
