Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:49.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很口渴 我就像孩子般的容易脱水\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm really thirsty.I used to dehydrate as a kid.
