Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就是那种又浓又粘的--  - 我去给你弄他妈的咖啡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- It was all thick and gooey-- - I'll get your fucking coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:57.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便给我也冲一杯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Get me one, too, while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:03.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙太紧张了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That guy is tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧张足以致命\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tension is a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:08.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经加入过在伊利诺州邵崎市 的一个男声四重唱组合\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I used to be in a barbershop quartet in Skokie, Illinois.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:11.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男中音就叫基普・迪斯金， 大胖子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The baritone was this guy named Kip Diskin, big fat guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:14.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖的像逆戟鲸。他每天早上都紧张的要命--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Like, orca fat.He was so stressed in the morning--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:18.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道我们现在是想帮你  - 当然，我很感激\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You know we're trying to help you.- Sure, and I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:21.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想帮你，奎恩探员 我喜欢警察\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I wanna help you, Agent Kujan.I like cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:24.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾想成为联邦人员， 可是我的--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I would've liked to have been a fed,but my CP--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:28.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没跟我们完全交代 我知道你知道些事情\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're not tellin' us everything.I know you know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:30.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经全都对地方检察官说了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I told the DA everything I know.
