Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:38.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我明白你认为他是好人  - 我知道他很好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I know you think he's a good man. - I know he was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾是个贪污的警察\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He was a corrupt cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:43.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，15年前的事了，他还是个好贼\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sure. 15 years ago,but he was a good thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:45.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正条子们不让他做合法生意。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The cops wouldn't let him go legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:47.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪恩・基顿是一坨屎\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dean Keaton was a piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:53.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想从我身上得到点什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Are you trying to get a rise out of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:57.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我只想听听你的故事  - 全在那儿了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I just wanna hear your story. - It's all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能抽支烟吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}May I have a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:06.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 根据你的供述--  - 给个火\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- According to your statement-- - I need a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:12.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据你的供述， 你只是个小毛贼…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}According to your statement,you're a short-con operator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:14.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…不入流的--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...run-of-the-mill--
