Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:24.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…不入流的骗子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...run-of-the-mill scams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:27.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些应该已经被禁止了，里面的东西是不被承认的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's been suppressed.Anything in there is inadmissible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.60,0:24:30.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，你做了桩好交易，完全豁免\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know. Sweet deal you have here.Total immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.10,0:24:37.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被诉持械 还有六个月的日子得熬\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I do have the weapons charge.I'm lookin' at six whole months hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.60,0:24:39.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认识一个叫鲁比・迪莫的商人吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You know a dealer named Ruby Deemer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.10,0:24:43.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认识一个叫约翰・保罗的教徒吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You know a religious guy named John Paul?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.40,0:24:46.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 知道阿提卡（著名监狱）的鲁比吗？  - 我和他没什么瓜葛\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You know Ruby's in Attica? - He didn't have my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:48.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识鲁比，他很受人尊敬\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know Ruby. He's big on respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:50.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的好朋友，很喜欢我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's a good friend of mine,likes me very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.00,0:24:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知你的证供已被封存 可鲁比的关系很广\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know your testimony is sealed.Ruby's well connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.10,0:24:56.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有许多内部的朋友愿为他效力\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's got lots of friends inside who do favors for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.80,0:25:00.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他知道你把他的名字供给了地方检察官，他会怎么说呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What would he say if he found out you dropped his name to the DA?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.00,0:25:04.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 上面根本没提鲁比的事   - 可我会这么对他说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- There's nothing there on Ruby. - I'll be sure to mention that to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.50,0:25:07.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我从这行学了什么？ 就是如何认出凶手\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Know what I've learned on the job?How to spot a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.70,0:25:10.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就说你抓了一宗谋杀案的三个疑犯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Say you arrest three guys for the same killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.10,0:25:11.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把他们关通宵\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Put them in jail overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.60,0:25:14.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了第二天早上， 谁要是睡着了，谁就是凶手\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Next morning,whoever's sleeping is your man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.00,0:25:17.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你犯了罪，等到被捕 你的戒心就松懈了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you're guilty, you know you're caught.You let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.80,0:25:20.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-  你听得懂吗？  - 不\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You follow me? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.30,0:25:21.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我直说重点吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let me get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.70,0:25:27.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比你聪明， 我会查出我要知道的事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm smarter than you,and I'm gonna find out what I wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.80,0:25:30.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会查出来的，无论你喜不喜欢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll get it, whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.30,0:25:32.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是告密的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm not a rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:40.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.70,0:25:48.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在危地马拉摘咖啡豆的时候曾经做过新鲜咖啡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When I was pickin' beans in Guatemala we used to make fresh coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.50,0:25:51.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是直接从树上摘下的，好喝极了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Right off the trees, I mean. That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.70,0:25:55.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这简直是屎，不过我是在警局里   - 我们能继续吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- This is shit, but I'm in a police station. - Can we get started again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.60,0:25:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指认结束后怎样了？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What happened after the lineup?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.80,0:26:06.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那值班的中士对我说不能释放你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The desk sergeant was telling me he couldn't release you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.80,0:26:10.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能相信吗？你甚至未被起诉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Can you believe that?You weren't even charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.00,0:26:11.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的警察\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Damn police.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.10,0:26:16.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你的脸拍照\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I wanna have pictures taken of your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.70,0:26:19.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明天就送到地方检察官那儿   - 算了吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'll take them to the DA tomorrow. - Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.80,0:26:22.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不行。星期一我就会把这事报到大陪审团去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll have this thing in front of a grand jury by Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.70,0:26:24.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再谈这事了，好吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't want to talk about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.60,0:26:29.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗提和雷诺怎么说？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What did Fortier and Renault say?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:32.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们需要多些时间考虑投资\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They asked for more time to think about investing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.70,0:26:33.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.30,0:26:35.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要多些时间干什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}More time for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.90,0:26:39.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论你怎么掩盖我的历史 他们还是会查到我的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No matter how you cover my tracks they're still gonna find out about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.90,0:26:41.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我点信心\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Give me some credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:44.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你撇开这事的，我们去找大陪审团\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I got you this far.Let's go to the grand jury.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.30,0:26:48.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 如果不这样，这事不会停--   - 这永远不会停，句号。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- This isn't gonna stop if we don't-- - It's never going to stop, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.00,0:26:53.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下星期所有投资者都将离弃我们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}By next week, every investor in the city is gonna be walking away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.80,0:26:56.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事完了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.30,0:26:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:05.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别轻言放弃，基顿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't give up on me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.70,0:27:09.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这永远也不会停\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's never gonna stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.90,0:27:18.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.40,0:27:21.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们今晚毁了我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They ruined me in there tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.70,0:27:25.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.60,0:27:27.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.00,0:27:34.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（寻狗启事）\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.00,0:27:36.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.70,0:27:40.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.10,0:27:43.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去我家吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's just go to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.40,0:28:00.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们明天再操心这些。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We'll worry about this tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.50,0:28:06.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.60,0:28:11.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芬斯特和麦克马纳斯有个精明的提议:\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fenster and McManus had a cagey proposition:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.40,0:28:13.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快速行动，高风险，利润也大\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A fast-jump, high-risk, long money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.40,0:28:16.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都知道那行得通\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We all knew it could be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.20,0:28:19.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我琢磨这事办坏了就意味着杀人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The way I figured,to do it wrong meant killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.20,0:28:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要办好就得五个人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}To do it right took five men.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.90,0:28:23.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五个人意味着基顿加入\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Five men meant Keaton.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.00,0:28:26.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基顿令人信服\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keaton took convincing.
