Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.50,0:50:44.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那么这个律师--   - 小林\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- So this lawyer-- - Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.20,0:50:47.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是瑞德福特引来的？  - 对\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Came from Redfoot. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.90,0:50:50.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和地方检察官说的时候为何漏了这段？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And why leave this out when you talked to the DA?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.80,0:50:52.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴夫，有人找你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dave, someone to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.20,0:51:00.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我满世界找你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.40,0:51:04.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在找昨晚大屠杀失踪的可卡因？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You still after that coke that took a walk out of that bloodbath yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.10,0:51:06.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用查了，没有可卡因\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You can stop looking. There was no coke.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.00,0:51:10.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在州立医院找到了一个从排水管道救上的人…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've been in LA County talking to a guy they pulled out of a drainpipe...
