Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.50,0:51:14.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早他苏醒了，开始说话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He came to this morning,he started talking.
