Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.80,0:51:24.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是有--  - 我知道.可他说没有毒品\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- But there were-- - We know. But he says no on the dope.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.10,0:51:27.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这匈牙利人告诉我，他们第二天要去土耳其\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This Hungarian tells me they were pulling stumps for Turkey the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.70,0:51:31.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没时间做那种货 也无意运毒\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They had no time for that kind of product,and no means to move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.40,0:51:33.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那钱是做什么的？  - 他不知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What's the money for? - He didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.80,0:51:36.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了几个关键人物，做事的没人知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No one doing the deal knew except for a few key people.
