Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.30,0:51:43.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 无论那是什么，都牵连重大   - 我不太明白\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Whatever it was, it was very sensitive. - I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.60,0:51:45.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个跛脚的纽约人在你这吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You got the cripple in there from New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.90,0:51:47.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他提过凯撒・苏斯没？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Did he mention Keyser Soze?
