Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.70,0:51:51.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心听我说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Just bear with me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.00,0:51:55.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁是凯撒・苏斯？ -操！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Who's Keyser Soze? - Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.80,0:52:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们讨论这个都一个半小时了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've been goin' over this for an hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.40,0:52:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需要找到瑞德福特 然后离开这鬼地方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What we need to do is find Redfoot and get the hell out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.40,0:52:06.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要做的是思考\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What we need to do is think.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.70,0:52:08.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回想一下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.20,0:52:12.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个实力人物…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Somebody with power...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.50,0:52:15.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…一个有能力从纽约到洛杉矶追踪我们的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...somebody capable of tracking us from New York to LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.70,0:52:18.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们在这儿干什么鬼事？  - 我们在等\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What the hell are we doing here? - We're waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.40,0:52:23.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 坐下   - 不，我火着呢，他妈的烦透了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Sit down. - No. I'm hot, and I'm fuckin' bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.30,0:52:25.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克内先生，停下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr.Hockney, do stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.90,0:52:27.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基顿先生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr.Keaton.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.60,0:52:29.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芬斯特先生，我从档案照片认出他…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr.Fenster I recognize from his mug shots...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.00,0:52:31.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…麦克马纳斯先生也是\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...as well as Mr.McManus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.90,0:52:36.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能猜你就是肯特先生，干掉索尔・伯格的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I can only assume that you are Mr.Kint,the gentleman who disposed of Saul Berg.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.00,0:52:40.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的雇主致上他的感谢，一份意想不到的好处\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My employer sends his gratitude,a most unexpected benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.90,0:52:43.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是小林先生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I am Mr.Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.80,0:52:48.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的雇主要我带份建议给你们几位先生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I have been asked by my employer to bring a proposal to you gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.60,0:52:51.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你想怎样？  - 我雇主想你们为他效劳\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What do you want? - My employer requires your services.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.80,0:52:57.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一趟活儿，工作一天，非常危险\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One job, one day's work. Very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.60,0:53:01.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没预计你们全部能活命，但活下来的…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He does not expect all of you to live.But those of you who do...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.20,0:53:05.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…可以分得九千一百万，怎么合适怎么分\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...will have $91 million to divide between you in any way you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.40,0:53:07.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你的老板？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Who's your boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.20,0:53:10.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为凯撒・苏斯做事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I work for Keyser Soze.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.20,0:53:23.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁是凯撒・苏斯？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Who's Keyser Soze?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.50,0:53:25.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个忽然冒出来的灵感\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Judging by the sudden change in mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.10,0:53:29.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…感觉你的合伙人可以告诉你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...I feel sure the rest of your associates can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.20,0:53:32.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带来一个苏斯先生直接提出的建议\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I come with an offer directly from Mr.Soze.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.40,0:53:36.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是个命令，实际上  - 你什么意思，“命令”？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- An order, actually. - What do you mean, "an order"?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.30,0:53:41.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1981年，你在纽约巴弗洛区参与骑劫一辆货车\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}In 1981, you participated in the hijacking of a truck in Buffalo, New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.90,0:53:45.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,货物是原钢材料，原属于苏斯先生…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The cargo was raw steel,steel which belonged to Mr.Soze...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.60,0:53:49.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…本应送到巴基斯坦作核反应堆\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and which was destined for Pakistan to be used in a nuclear reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.00,0:53:53.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是违反联合国条例的大生意\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A most profitable violation of UN Regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.10,0:53:55.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没办法知道这个，基顿先生...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You had no way of knowing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.30,0:53:58.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为船运这批钢材的人为苏斯先生效劳\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...because the fellow shipping the steel was working for Soze...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.50,0:54:00.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也毫不知情\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...without his knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.40,0:54:03.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年初，芬斯特先生与麦克马纳斯先生…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Earlier this year,Mr.Fenster and Mr.McManus...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.20,0:54:06.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在纽瓦克机场骑劫了一架双螺旋桨货机\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...hijacked a two-prop cargo flight out of Newark airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.00,0:54:11.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机上载有黄金和铂金丝，也是给巴基斯坦的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The plane was carrying gold and platinum wiring also set for Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.90,0:54:15.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个月前，霍克内先生偷了辆货车…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Two months ago,Mr.Hockney stole a truck...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.40,0:54:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…装着枪械零件，途经皇后区\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...carrying gun parts through Queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.10,0:54:21.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪零件本要由纽约州政府销毁\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Gun parts which were set to be destroyed by the state of New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.90,0:54:25.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们在一个中途站丢失了，并被转送贝尔法斯特\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They were to be lost in a way station and rerouted to Belfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.80,0:54:28.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又一次，苏斯先生利用了不知情的卒子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Again, Mr.Soze using pawns who had no knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.10,0:54:31.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就找到了肯特先生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Which brings us to Mr.Kint.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.50,0:54:35.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九个月前，苏斯先生的…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Nine months ago, one of Mr.Soze's...
