Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.40,0:54:41.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…是一个跛子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...by a cripple.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.20,0:54:44.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被骗去六万二千元\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He was relieved of $62,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.30,0:54:48.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花些时间才找齐你们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now, it has taken us some time to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.60,0:54:52.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来意图在纽约你们被捕后找你们的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Our intention was to approach you after your apprehension in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.70,0:54:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你安排的指认\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You set up the lineup.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.10,0:54:57.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.我没去见你们前，你们本不会被释放\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yes. You were not to be released until I had come to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.40,0:55:00.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来基顿先生的律师，芬纳兰小姐...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It seems Mr.Keaton's attorney,Miss Finneran...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.60,0:55:04.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…过于有效率地促成了他的释放。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...was a little too effective in expediting his release.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.20,0:55:06.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再留着你们其他人就没有意义了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Holding the rest of you became a moot point.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.70,0:55:09.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那瑞德福特呢？  - 瑞德福特先生一无所知\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What about Redfoot? - Mr.Redfoot knew nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.60,0:55:12.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏斯先生很少长久用同一批人工作...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr.Soze rarely works with the same people for long...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.30,0:55:15.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...而他们从不知道是为谁工作\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and they never know who they're working for.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.20,0:55:18.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有手下，就不会被出卖\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One cannot be betrayed if one has no people.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.10,0:55:21.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么告诉我们？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So, why are you telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.50,0:55:25.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们偷过苏斯先生，芬斯特先生。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Because you have stolen from Mr.Soze,Mr.Fenster.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.00,0:55:27.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们所有人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.10,0:55:30.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只因为你们不知道这一点，你们才活着\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That you did not know it is the only reason you're still alive.
