Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.50,0:55:39.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他妈的债，草泥马，我们怎知道你是为苏斯工作？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fuck the debt, and fuck you.How do we know you work for Soze?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.80,0:55:42.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这没太大关系，霍克内先生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't think that is very relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.50,0:55:45.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们五个要对索尔・伯格之死负责…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All five of you are responsible for the murder of Saul Berg...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.70,0:55:47.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…还有他的保镖\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and his bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.40,0:55:49.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞德福特先生可以作证\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr.Redfoot can testify to your involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.15,0:55:52.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道他会这么做的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We can see to it that he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.00,0:55:55.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你想说什么？  - 建议是这样的，先生们:\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What's your point? - The offer is this, gentlemen:
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.40,0:55:57.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏斯先生的主要兴趣\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr.Soze's primary interest...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.90,0:55:59.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…是毒品\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...is narcotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.60,0:56:04.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以说，有一个阿根廷集团，数年来一直在跟他竞争\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He has been competing, shall we say with a group of Argentineans for several years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.90,0:56:07.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与苏斯先生竞争已让他们损失惨重\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Competing with Mr.Soze has taken its toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.60,0:56:11.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些阿根廷人正在商谈…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}These Argentineans are negotiating the sale...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.20,0:56:15.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…一笔九千一百万元的可卡因买卖\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...of $91 million in cocaine in three days time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.40,0:56:21.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用说，这次采购将复活他们已经式微的组织\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Needless to say,this purchase will revitalize the diminishing strength of their organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.90,0:56:25.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏斯先生想你们制止这次买卖\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr.Soze would like you to stop the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.40,0:56:29.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果愿意，你们可以等买卖完成后动手\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you choose,you may wait until after the buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.20,0:56:31.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换手多少钱都是你们的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Whatever money changes hands is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.70,0:56:37.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏斯先生想你们上船，在船上销毁可卡因\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr.Soze would like you to get to the boat and destroy the cocaine onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.20,0:56:42.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此后你们就不欠他债了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And then you will be free of your obligations to Mr.Soze.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.40,0:56:48.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给个好理由，教我现在不杀你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Give me one good reason why I shouldn't kill you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.00,0:56:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏斯先生给你们的礼物\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A gift from Mr.Soze.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.80,0:56:57.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日安，先生们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Good day, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.80,0:57:43.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（芬斯特）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.40,0:58:10.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们这里有我一生的资料，从我十八岁后干的每一件事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They got my whole life in here,everything I've done since I was 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.30,0:58:12.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们他妈的什么都知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They fuckin' know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.60,0:58:15.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一个跟我一起干过活或者坐过牢的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Everybody I've ever worked with or did time with.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.80,0:58:30.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.10,0:58:35.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这事不对劲   - 我不知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- This isn't right. - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.40,0:58:38.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约那个曾经说起过苏斯的人是谁？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Who's that guy who used to talk about Soze in New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.20,0:58:44.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 布里克・马林  - 他为他做事，间接的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Bricks Marlin. - He did jobs for him, indirect stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.90,0:58:48.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他总是能得到超出他干的活五倍的钱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He said he always made five times more money on it than the job was worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.30,0:58:51.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙只是个幻影\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This guy's a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.10,0:58:53.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小林利用他作掩护\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kobayashi's using him\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}for window dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.80,0:58:55.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，这不好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't know. This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.90,0:58:59.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是鬼扯.这人可能是洛杉矶警察。这是他妈的圈套\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's bullshit. This guy could be LAPD.It's a fuckin' setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.70,0:59:03.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从我听说的来看，苏斯是那种屠夫杀人狂\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The way I hear it,Soze's some kind of butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.90,0:59:08.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是个变态无比的他妈的屠夫  - 没有凯撒・苏斯！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- A peerless, psycho, fucked-up butcher. - There is no Keyser Soze!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.90,0:59:12.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯撒・苏斯是谁？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Who is Keyser Soze?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.70,0:59:17.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应该是个土耳其人 有人说他父亲是德国人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's supposed to be Turkish.Some say his father was German.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.60,0:59:19.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从没人相信他是真实存在的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Nobody ever believed he was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.90,0:59:23.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人认识他，或见过直接为他工作的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Nobody knew him or saw anybody that ever worked directly for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.20,0:59:26.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按小林的说法，人人都可能为苏斯工作过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}To hear Kobayashi tell it,anybody could have worked for Soze.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.30,0:59:29.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你无从得知。那就是他的厉害\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You never knew. That was his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.20,0:59:36.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼耍过的最大的花招就是其令世人相信他不存在\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The greatest trick the Devil ever pulled was convincing the world he didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.75,0:59:36.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.90,0:59:40.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些伙计们告诉我的一个故事，我相信...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One story the guys told me,the story I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.70,0:59:42.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...那是他在土耳其时发生的事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...was from his days in Turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.50,0:59:45.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一帮匈牙利人想要开山立柜，\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There was a gang of Hungarians that wanted their own mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.50,0:59:48.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道想有势力，并不需要用枪…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They realized that to be in power,you didn't need guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.90,0:59:50.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…金钱，甚至不需要人多\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...or money or even numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.60,0:59:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只需要有决心做其他人不敢做的事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You just needed the will to do what the other guy wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.40,0:59:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久，他们有了势力，赶上了苏斯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}After a while they come into power,and then they come after Soze.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.90,1:00:01.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他当时规模小。只是经营毒品，他们说的。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He was small-time then.Just running dope, they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.50,1:00:07.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午，他们闯进他家，要抢他的生意\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They come to his home in the afternoon looking for his business.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.90,1:00:12.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在房子里找到他的妻儿，决定等苏斯回来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They find his wife and kids in the house,and decide to wait for Soze.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.00,1:00:32.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他回到家，发现妻子被强奸，孩子们在哭喊\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He comes home to find his wife raped and children screaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.30,1:00:35.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匈牙利人知道苏斯凶狠，不是可以愚弄的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The Hungarians knew Soze was tough,not to be trifled with.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.80,1:00:37.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们让他知道他们是冲着生意来的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They let him know they meant business.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.60,1:00:40.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.00,1:00:46.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说想要他的地盘，以及他所有的生意\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They tell him they want his territory,all his business.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.90,1:00:50.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏斯环顾家人的脸\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Soze looks over the faces of his family.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.30,1:00:56.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后向这些有决心的人展示什么是真正的决心\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Then he showed these men of will what will really was.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.30,1:01:18.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉他们他情愿看着家人死去…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He tells them he would rather see his family dead...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.70,1:01:21.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是此后继续偷生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...than live another day after this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.50,1:01:24.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他放走最后那个匈牙利人…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He lets the last Hungarian go...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.80,1:01:28.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等妻儿入土后，追踪这班党徒逐一报复\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...waits until his family is in the ground,and goes after the rest of the mob.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.20,1:01:31.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了他们的孩子，杀了他们的妻子…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He kills their kids, he kills their wives...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.00,1:01:34.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…杀了他们的父母及其朋友\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...he kills their parents and their friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.70,1:01:36.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧掉他们的居所…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He burns down the houses they live in...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.10,1:01:39.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…及他们工作的店铺\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and the stores they work in.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.30,1:01:43.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了那些欠他们钱的人。然后就像这样…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He kills people that owe them money.And like that...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.20,1:01:47.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…他消失了，转入地下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...he's gone, underground.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.10,1:01:49.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自此再没人见过他。他成了一个神话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Nobody's ever seen him since.He becomes a myth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.70,1:01:52.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个罪犯们晚上给孩子说的鬼故事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A spook story that criminals tell their kids at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.00,1:01:56.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“要是不听话，凯撒・苏斯就会来抓你”\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}"Rat on your pop,and Keyser Soze will get you."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.00,1:01:59.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人相信这事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No one ever really believes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.20,1:02:01.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信有这人吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do you believe in him?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.80,1:02:05.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基顿总是说:\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keaton always said:
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.80,1:02:09.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我不信上帝，但我怕他”\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}"I don't believe in God,but I'm afraid of him."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.20,1:02:13.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信上帝\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.40,1:02:17.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一让我恐惧的就是凯撒・苏斯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And the only thing that scares me is Keyser Soze.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.30,1:02:26.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这你当回事吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You give any weight to this?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.40,1:02:28.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以给你介绍法院的丹・曼厮固\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I can introduce you to Dan Metzheiser from Justice.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.00,1:02:32.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有份苏斯在华盛顿的文件。这段时间已经成了他的爱好了。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's got a file on Soze in DC.It's been a hobby of his for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.70,1:02:36.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人视他为《无敌浩克》 中的那个记者\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A lot of guys equate him to that reporter on The Incredible Hulk.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.20,1:02:42.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听过他的事？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You've heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.70,1:02:44.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿？道上？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Where? On the street?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.60,1:02:47.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有几次，你知道，外围传言\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A few times. You know, outside stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.60,1:02:51.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某人替某个为某个从苏斯那里拿钱的人工作。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Someone working for a guy who worked for a guy who got money from Soze.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.70,1:02:53.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一类的屁话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Shit like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.10,1:02:56.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可能是一种古老的标记，一种符印\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It could be an old badge. A hex sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.40,1:02:59.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个莫测的名字，会让人不敢搞你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keep people from fucking with you when a name meant something.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.60,1:03:01.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但你来了   - 妈的，没错\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- But you're here. - Shit, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.80,1:03:06.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙想从医院里逃走，就因为害怕苏斯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This guy's trying to walk out of a hospital because he's so afraid of Soze.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.70,1:03:08.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会探个虚实的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll run it up the flagpole.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.20,1:03:12.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是清白的。事情怎样我就怎讲。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I came clean. I told it like it happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.80,1:03:14.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么去的那儿又有什么关系？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So what about how I got there?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.40,1:03:17.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的话满是漏洞，地方检察官早就告诉我别指望特赦了。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's so full of holes, the DA would've told me to forget amnesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.70,1:03:19.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想从我这知道的也得到了。又怎样。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You got what you wanted out of me.Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.00,1:03:22.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那就是你没告诉地方检察官的原因？  - 你说呢…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- That's why you never told the DA? - You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.00,1:03:26.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我告诉你是尼斯湖怪雇的我，你会怎么说？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If I told you the Loch Ness monster hired me, what would you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.30,1:03:28.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做污点证人，我们会召你作证\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Turn state's evidence.We'll put you on the stand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.60,1:03:31.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经豁免了。你还能给我开什么条件？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've got immunity.What can you possibly offer me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.20,1:03:34.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若真有凯撒・苏斯其人，他会来找你的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If there really is a Keyser Soze,he's gonna come lookin' for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.30,1:03:36.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有大脑？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Where's your head?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.10,1:03:39.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为压力来自何方？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Where do you think the pressure is?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.00,1:03:42.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯撒・苏斯，或者你怎么称呼他都行，知道我现在在哪\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keyser Soze, or whatever you call him,knows where I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.40,1:03:46.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有办法捅你屁股，因此他十分钟内就能把我捞出去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He has the burner on your ass to let me go so he can scoop me up 10 minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.80,1:03:48.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豁免权也就是跟你们这些混球交易罢了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Immunity was just a deal with you assholes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.90,1:03:50.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我被保释出去，就有了新麻烦\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I got a new problem when I post bail.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.90,1:03:53.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何让他玩弄于股掌？我们能保护你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why play into his hands?We can protect you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.40,1:03:57.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了，戴夫。到现在为止你干得很好。威逼利诱。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thanks, Dave. Bang-up job so far.Extortion, coercion.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.80,1:03:59.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我要你舔我的屁股，请原谅。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Pardon me if I ask you to kiss my pucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.00,1:04:03.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整得我们走投无路的那群混蛋，正是现在保释我的人。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The same fuckers that rounded us up are now bailing me out?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.40,1:04:05.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.00,1:04:09.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你能逮住凯撒・苏斯？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You think you can catch Keyser Soze?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.50,1:04:14.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为像他这样的人会让你接近，让你抓住，揪出他的脑袋来？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You think a guy like that comes this close to getting caught and sticks his head out?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.30,1:04:17.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若他真要来，那就是为了除掉我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If he comes up for anything,it'll be to get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.40,1:04:19.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那以后…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}After that...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.40,1:04:22.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…我的看法是你再也听不到他的消息了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...my guess is you'll never hear from him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.40,1:04:46.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来怎样了？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.30,1:04:49.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天我们醒来，芬斯特已经走了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We woke up the next morning and Fenster was gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.10,1:04:51.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被苏斯整垮的念头让他受不了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He couldn't handle the idea of slumming for Soze.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.90,1:04:53.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他留下字条祝我们好运…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He left us a note wishing us good luck...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.90,1:04:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…还拿走了大部分我们凑起来的钱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and took a chunk of the money we'd scraped together.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.70,1:04:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后怎样？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.10,1:04:59.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克马纳斯很狂躁\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}McManus was furious.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.60,1:05:03.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说要抓他回来扯出他的心。那一类的屁话。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He talked about tracking him down and ripping his heart out. All sorts of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.60,1:05:06.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上，我们接到那个电话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That night, we got the call.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.10,1:05:08.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么电话？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What call?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.50,1:05:10.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小林告诉我们哪里能找到芬斯特\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kobayashi told us where we could find Fenster.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.10,1:05:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们快他妈的离开这儿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.00,1:05:24.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得把他埋了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We gotta bury him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.70,1:05:26.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}With what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.50,1:05:28.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我们的手\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}With our hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.90,1:05:39.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是发神经\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is nuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.50,1:05:41.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他妈的干沙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's dry fucking sand.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.60,1:05:45.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他腐烂时 那些冲浪者一里外也能闻到\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When he rots the surfers\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}are gonna smell him a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.20,1:05:47.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 挖，你他妈的  - 我们该怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Dig, you fuck. - What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.30,1:05:49.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙会他妈杀了我们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This fuckin' guy is gonna kill us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.30,1:05:53.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你，拐脚，但我能跑。这我没问题\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't know about you, peg leg,but I can run. I got no problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.00,1:05:57.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来小林对此也没什么问题\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kobayashi doesn't seem to have a problem with it either.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.10,1:06:00.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跑了，我们就要为你挖一个坑\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You run, and we're gonna be diggin' a hole for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.00,1:06:02.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You got that?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.10,1:06:06.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们埋的又不是我亲儿子。我不欠任何人的！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This ain't my boy we're burying.I don't owe anybody!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.40,1:06:11.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去你的吧  - 他跟我搭档五年了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- So fuck you. - He was my partner for five years.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.30,1:06:14.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们干过的活、我见过的钱比你想象的还多\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We did more jobs and I saw more money than you can ever count.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.80,1:06:16.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈去死！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.80,1:06:19.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以现在才要还债！  - 这不是还债！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- 'Cause now it's payback! - It's not payback!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.80,1:06:24.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是警告\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's precaution.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.60,1:06:27.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想还债？你想跑路？我不在乎\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You want payback? You wanna run?I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.60,1:06:32.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是为芬斯特做\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm not doin' this for Fenster.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.60,1:06:35.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是为你们做\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm not doin' it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.00,1:06:38.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为我自己做\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm doin' this for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.70,1:06:42.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要了结这事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm gonna finish this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.30,1:06:46.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让这叫小林的杂种活下去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This Kobayashi bastard is not gonna stand on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.70,1:07:09.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芬斯特被杀后，没有人逃跑？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}After they killed Fenster,nobody would run?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.90,1:07:13.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想的，我想我们能逃脱   - 那你怎么不说？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I wanted to. I thought we could make it. - Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.90,1:07:16.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我，我试了， 但基顿不同意这么做\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Believe me, I tried,but Keaton wouldn't have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.60,1:07:18.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他来说太牵强\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It was too far-fetched for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.70,1:07:21.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基顿是个脚踏实地的人，前警察\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keaton was a grounded guy. An ex-cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.10,1:07:24.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于警察来说，从来没有复杂的解释\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}To a cop, the explanation is never that complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.10,1:07:25.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是很简单\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's always simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.80,1:07:28.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道上的传说不是真的，幕后黑手不存在\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's no mystery to the street,no arch-criminal.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.40,1:07:32.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见具尸体，心想是他兄弟干的。可能真就是。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You got a body and think his brother did it, you're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.30,1:07:33.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人与基顿争论\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Nobody argued with Keaton.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.80,1:07:36.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们下决心打败小林\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They just set their minds to whacking Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.50,1:07:47.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们上来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're coming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.60,1:07:53.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听到了吗？他上来了  - 他正下来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Did you hear me? He's coming up. - He's on his way down.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.40,1:08:51.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.50,1:08:54.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按二十楼，马上\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Press 20. Do it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.50,1:09:15.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.00,1:09:21.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们的答复是“不行”   - 苏斯先生会很--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- The answer is "no." - Mr.Soze will be most--
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.00,1:09:24.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，混蛋 根本没有凯撒・苏斯这个人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Listen, cocksucker,there is no Keyser Soze.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.30,1:09:26.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要再提这名字，我立刻就杀了你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mention his name again,I'll kill you right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.80,1:09:30.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪的威胁，我以为你们来这里怎么都要杀了我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A strange threat. I assume you've come here to kill me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.20,1:09:38.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你找得到我们…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We know that you can get to us...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.50,1:09:42.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…可现在你也知道了 我们能找到你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...but now you know that we can get to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.90,1:09:45.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最后给你次机会去终止此事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm giving you one last chance to call this off.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.40,1:09:49.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的雇主已经下了决心\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My employer has made up his mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.50,1:09:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他不会改变主意的   - 我们也不会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- He does not change it. - Neither do we.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.80,1:09:55.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了芬斯特， 但你杀不了我们所有人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You got Fenster,but you won't be able to get all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.70,1:09:58.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少在我们中的某个干掉你之前不会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not before one of us gets through to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.10,1:10:01.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信你的话，真心实意地信\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I believe you. I most sincerely do.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.10,1:10:04.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你们不是有能耐的人， 就不会被选中\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You would not have been chosen were you not so suitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.90,1:10:08.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能做这决定。无论你们拿什么来威胁我…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But I cannot make this decision.Whatever you threaten me with is...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.90,1:10:11.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…跟我不能完全执行命令而遭到的惩罚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...ludicrous in comparison to what will be done to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.80,1:10:14.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…比起来都是小菜一碟\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...if I do not carry out my orders in full.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.90,1:10:24.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要杀你的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm the guy that's gonna get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.10,1:10:28.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想你知道那点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I just wanted you to know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.20,1:10:31.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.70,1:10:34.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恳求你，相信我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I implore you, believe me...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.60,1:10:36.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,… 苏斯先生确有其人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...Mr.Soze is very real...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.00,1:10:39.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- …而他是个很坚决的人   - 我们等着瞧吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- ...and very determined. - We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.90,1:10:50.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你干掉我之前…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Before you do me in...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.80,1:10:54.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…你们会允许我先去了结与芬纳兰小姐的公事，对吧？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...you will let me finish my business with Miss Finneran first, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.70,1:11:01.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.30,1:11:03.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊迪・芬纳兰\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Edie Finneran.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.20,1:11:06.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她正在楼上我的办公室…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}She's upstairs in my office...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.80,1:11:09.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…等着交涉一桩引渡案\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...for an extradition deposition.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.00,1:11:12.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要求她亲自来谈这案子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I requested she be\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}put on the case personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.90,1:11:14.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是昨天飞来的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}She flew in yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.70,1:11:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.50,1:11:20.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kill away.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.20,1:11:26.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谎\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.20,1:11:28.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.80,1:11:49.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芬纳兰小姐在洛杉矶期间有人陪护\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Miss Finneran's escort while she's here in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.50,1:11:51.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,片刻不离\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Never leaves her for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.50,1:11:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你会高兴有好手保护着她\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I thought you'd be glad to know she's in good hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.80,1:12:01.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息会儿吧 船在星期五到\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Get some rest.The boat will be ready for you on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.70,1:12:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那之前我见到你或你的朋友\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If I see you or any of your friends before then...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.40,1:12:09.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…芬纳兰小姐死前会遭受最可怕的污辱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...Miss Finneran will be the victim of a most gruesome violation before she dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.40,1:12:11.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲也一样，霍克内先生…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}As indeed will your father, Mr.Hockney...
