Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.20,1:12:19.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能只会阉掉麦克马纳斯先生的侄子，戴维。\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I might only castrate Mr.McManus' nephew, David.
