Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.90,1:12:27.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会处理楼下那两具尸体\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We will take care of the two bodies downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.50,1:12:29.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并会把账算到芬斯特先生身上\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We'll add them to the cost of Mr.Fenster.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.60,1:12:32.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请恕失陪，先生们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you'll excuse me, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.00,1:13:13.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常难安排\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's a logistical nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.30,1:13:16.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近距离，10到20个人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Close quarters. 10, maybe 20 men.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.70,1:13:19.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道甲板下还有多少人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's no tellin' how many more are gonna be below deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.70,1:13:21.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能偷袭那些家伙吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Can we stealth these guys?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.30,1:13:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么多可卡因，他们会小心防范的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}With all that coke, they're gonna be ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.30,1:13:28.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这带给我们另一个问题\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Which brings me to sunny point Number 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.30,1:13:32.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我们有人能杀进去并劫走那船 还是什么也得不到\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Even if one of us gets through and jacks the boat, we still got nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.90,1:13:34.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他们收了钱呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What if we wait for the money?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.20,1:13:37.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那至少又多了十个人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Ten more men at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.80,1:13:40.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依我看，干不了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}In my opinion, it can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.00,1:13:43.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁进去了都不会活着出来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Anyone who goes in is not comin' out alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.30,1:13:46.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会等钱到再下手  - 我也是\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'm gonna wait for the money. - Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.40,1:13:49.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们听见他刚才的话吗？  - 反正必须去，我得拿一份\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Did you hear what he just said? - If I'm goin' in, I want a cut.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.90,1:13:51.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.70,1:13:54.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有办不成的事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's nothing that can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.70,1:14:01.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我简直不敢相信，我们就这么去送死\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I just can't believe we're gonna walk in to certain death.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.60,1:14:10.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电台里说纽约正在下雨\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The news said it's raining in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.90,1:14:33.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么语言？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What language is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.70,1:14:36.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道。俄语，我想\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't know. Russian, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.80,1:14:40.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匈牙利语\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hungarian?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.30,1:15:46.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包裹到了，先生们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The package has arrived, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.80,1:16:07.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子们准备好了吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You kids ready?
