Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.10,1:16:16.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克马纳斯，你最好在十秒内到位\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}McManus, you better be set up in 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.00,1:16:19.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.80,1:16:22.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你留在这里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I want you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.60,1:16:24.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来要掩护--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm supposed to cover--
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.00,1:16:27.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们出不来了，带上钱走\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If we don't get out of this,take the money and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.90,1:16:29.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I can't--
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.00,1:16:31.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找伊迪 把事情全都告诉她\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Find Edie.Tell her everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.50,1:16:33.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她认识许多人 她知道该如何处理\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}She knows people. She knows what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.60,1:16:36.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果用我的方法除不掉小林，那么她有她的办法做到\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If I don't get Kobayashi my way,she'll get him her way.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.70,1:16:39.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可要是我--   - 按我说的去做\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What if I-- - Just do what I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.90,1:16:41.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.40,1:16:46.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她….\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tell her that...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.60,1:16:51.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她我已经尽力了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tell her I tried.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.40,1:17:06.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克马纳斯，他过来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}McManus, he's on his way.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.30,1:17:08.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经就位\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.80,1:18:04.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一，二，三，四…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.20,1:18:07.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…五，六，七…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...five, six, seven...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.30,1:18:10.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯瓦德的活不好干啊\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oswald was a fag.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.40,1:18:20.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.10,1:18:22.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.50,1:18:27.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.40,1:18:54.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.60,1:19:27.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克唐纳先生有块地\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}"Old McDonald had a farm
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.90,1:19:30.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊呀，伊呀，哟\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}"Ee-aye, ee-aye, O
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.00,1:19:35.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“在那地里他杀了班人”\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}"And on that farm, he shot some guys"
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.00,1:20:10.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猫王要出场了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Elvis has left the building.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.80,1:21:24.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪，别开枪.自己人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hold fire. Hold fire. Vamonos!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.10,1:21:39.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.70,1:22:35.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何不逃？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.90,1:22:37.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被吓呆了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I froze up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.00,1:22:41.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了芬斯特，他被埋葬时的样子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I thought about Fenster and how he looked when we buried him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.40,1:22:45.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我又想到基顿，那时候看起来他可能圆满完成\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Then I thought about Keaton,and it looked like he might pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.70,1:22:53.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有个男孩在沙滩上发现一具尸体\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A boy found a body on the beach today.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.90,1:22:56.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是被人从船上抛下海的 头部中两枪\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thrown clear of the boat.Shot twice in the head.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.40,1:22:58.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局里的两个人去鉴定了他的身份\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Two guys from the Bureau identified him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.40,1:23:00.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还有呢？  - 他叫阿图罗・马克兹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What else? - His name was Arturo Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.70,1:23:02.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个阿根廷小走私犯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A petty smuggler from Argentina.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.70,1:23:05.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年在纽约曾因毒品交易被捕\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He was arrested last year in New York for trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.60,1:23:09.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他逃往加州，但在长滩被捉回\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He escapes to California.They pick him up in Long Beach.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.40,1:23:12.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们安排引渡他 他又逃了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're setting up extradition,he escapes again.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.90,1:23:14.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now, get this.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.30,1:23:17.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊迪・芬纳兰提出的引渡建议\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Edie Finneran's brought in to advise on the proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.15,1:23:19.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小林\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.30,1:23:21.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约传给了我一份他的证词\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}New York faxed me a copy of his testimony.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.60,1:23:24.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他是个告密者  - 是个他妈的大叛徒\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- He was a rat. - A big fucking rat.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.20,1:23:27.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿图罗很害怕回到监狱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Arturo was very opposed to returning to prison.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.10,1:23:31.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至于他供出了将近五十个人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So much so,that he named close to 50 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.20,1:23:33.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜最后的人名是谁？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Guess who he named in the finale.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.65,1:23:36.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯撒・苏斯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keyser Soze.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.30,1:23:37.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's more.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.00,1:23:54.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把所知一切告诉你 若说重覆了就告诉我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll tell you what I know.Stop me when this sounds familiar.
